title: No. 5 Virginia Tech vies to sweep Liberty on Wednesday - VT hokiesports.com
content: No. 5 Virginia Tech vies to sweep Liberty on Wednesday  VT hokiesports.com
description: Running into its first of two 30-win clubs this week, the No. 5 Virginia Tech baseball team (33-10) will pursue its regular season sweep of Liberty (30-16) on Wednesday, May 11, when the programs meet during midweek action at English Field at Atlantic Union Bank Park.
